The third album from Mercury Prize nominated, Geordie post-punkers Maximo Park was produced by Nick Cave/Grinderman/Yeah Yeah Yeahs producer Nick Launay, and comes four years after their last full-length studio release. Quicken The Heart is slightly darker and more groove-based than their previous efforts but overall continues the band's style of lyrically-intelligent indie-rock.
